 《通缉犯》的马克斯·乔治在圣诞节前及时出院https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-wanteds-max-george-discharged-from-hospital-in-time-for-christmas-3824744?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=the-wanteds-max-乔治在圣诞节前及时出院Emma WilkesTue, 24 Dec 2024 17:58:16 +0000 Music NewsNewsPop https://www.nme.com/?p=3824744 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/max-george-jeff-spicer-1.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="马克斯·乔治" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/max-george-jeff-spicer-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/max-george-jeff-spicer-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/max-george-jeff-spicer-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/max-george-jeff-spicer-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/max-george-jeff-spicer-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/max-george-jeff-spicer-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>乔治上周因心脏病入院后安装了起搏器</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-wanteds-max-george-discharged-from-hospital-in-time-for-christmas-3824744">《通缉犯》的马克斯·乔治在圣诞节期间及时出院的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/max-george-jeff-spicer-1.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="马克斯·乔治" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/max-george-jeff-spicer-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/max-george-jeff-spicer-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/max-george-jeff-spicer-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/max-george-jeff-spicer-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/max-george-jeff-spicer-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/max-george-jeff-spicer-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-wanted">《通缉犯</a>》的马克斯·乔治在<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-wanteds-max-george-has-pacemaker-fitted-3824553">安装起搏器后已出院。</a></p><p>本月早些时候，乔治透露， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-wanteds-max-george-in-hospital-with-heart-issues-3821994">一些检查显示他的心脏有“问题”，他已住院</a>。他解释说，他是在“感觉非常不适”并做了一些检查后才入院的。后来，他得知自己<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-wanteds-max-george-shares-health-update-from-hospital-bed-as-he-awaits-heart-surgery-3822594">因心脏病需要接受手术</a>。</p><p>这位 36 岁的老人<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-wanteds-max-george-shares-health-update-from-hospital-bed-as-he-awaits-heart-surgery-3822594">说，</a>他的心脏有“2:1 阻滞”，即心脏跳动比应有的速度更慢或更不规则。随后，他需要安装起搏器，这是一种小型电池供电的机器，通常植入胸部或腹部，以帮助控制不规则或缓慢的心率。</p><p>最初，他预计必须在医院度过圣诞节，但当他发现自己可以比预期更早进行手术时，情况发生了变化。</p><p>现在，乔治表示，在住院 11 天后，他将在圣诞节前及时出院。不过，他确实表示自己并不完全清楚，因为医生发现需要对他的肺部潜在问题进行更多调查。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/DD2KxTLoKBg/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 